full_text: Everyone’s fighting over twitter and I’m just here posting nothing of any real to use to any of them.
Leftist twitter isn't "melting down" over the idea of Elon buying it, these people are just their front lines for public opinion and support in the attack the establishment is about to roll out.
Just wait until puppets like Trudeau start blocking twitter in their country due to "security concerns."

A free speech platform won't be enough. Every leftist establishment shill who cheered censorship and profited from the corruption of Twitter's policies needs a lifetime ban, shunned from any semblance of participation in civil discussion.
The leftist panic on twitter over Musk is really just about their paychecks. Without the enforcement of censorship and rigged algorithms, they know they’ll be worthless.
Imagine a leftist walk out of twitter on a scale of even Neil Young couldn’t imagine.
Maybe Elon will buy Star Wars next.
